{"tid":1599304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問奪台邦交國有助小英選情   王毅臉色大變 :「這是什麼邏輯?」","createTime":"2019-09-28T02:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:00:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"34b97896fb78751b30a91167cb8eb004855ac85a","tid":1599304,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpGmyZeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpGmyZeT.jpg&h=e3fc6437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n在中國施壓下，我國近期被連奪兩邦交國，有記者詢問中國外長王毅，此舉是否反而有助總統蔡英文選情，王毅變臉回「這是什麼邏輯？」<br />\n<br />\n《世界日報》 報導，27日中國國務委員兼外長王毅與吉里巴斯總統兼外長馬茂（Taneti Maamau），在紐約中國駐聯合國代表團大樓簽署復交公報，兩人對外發言結束後，中國官員隨即對記者表示「No questions！」<br />\n<br />\n隨後現場《世界日報》記者大聲用中文詢問王毅是否能夠提問，王毅答應，但隨行人員不斷推擠記者。《世界日報》記者詢問，中國連續奪走台灣邦交國，台灣內部認為此舉「協助」蔡英文連任，且中國不再考慮民心感受。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，王毅對此瞬間回應「這是什麼邏輯」，記者再度詢問同樣問題，王毅便嚴肅地重複「這是什麼邏輯」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2929438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2929438&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9814df30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2929438&h=6406d150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2929438</a>"},{"pid":"695b1244c41ecc7d79f33b215048aa438d49b94d","tid":1599304,"uid":105976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"屌 個記者提左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51de96c2c831e871ab900565b4ea586bb59c655","tid":1599304,"uid":289946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"